<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A Lieng Ngei ie!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. A Lalna kumsawt gam chu taihsan in,
 Alang A vai A lieng eihaw dingin;
 Vangkhuo ah muong takin Lalpa A leng ngam puoi,
 Zie khawvel ahin chu lawih na ding A hung vai.

[V2]
 A um puoi I Lalpau banga lieng hi,
 Tu chan hin le I Hukdampau chu,
 Gitloh vangin lungkham, A lieng taluoi aw,
 Vakvaih sak puoi tiu.

[V3]
 2. Maltanga giekmawh vacha bangin maw,
 Lungakna mun nei loin maw Isu;
 Tuipi dung leh vai ah lieng takin Na vak hi,
 Lalpa, ka dah taluoi nei hehpihna ziekin.

[V4]
 3. Giloa a ngawhpau i Lalpau chu,
 Lal Pilat in thiemloh a chansak hi;
 Chawnban in a kai ui, kalvari lam zuon in,
 Tha a kie tai Isu kalvari tang chung ah.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>62</hymn_number>
</song>